      *    * Visualizzazione campo : Codice tipo operazione            *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-tip-ope-000.
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "N"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      04                   to   v-car                  .
           move      zero                 to   v-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-sgn                  .
           move      "<B"                 to   v-edm                  .
           move      05                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      22                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-tes-tip-ope        to   v-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
